      "rationale": "Testing conducted at a single load configuration (ASTM F1717 standard setup) and single crosshead displacement rate (5 mm/min). Environmental conditions documented (23±2°C, 50±5% RH). Only one test condition evaluated; does not span the COU parameter space. Achieved level (2) is below required level (3). This shortfall is acknowledged; the single condition corresponds to the regulatory standard and is considered acceptable for the intended submission scope, but represents a limitation of the validation dataset."
