      "rationale": "FEA boundary conditions replicate ASTM F1717 fixture geometry (loading nose radius, UHMWPE block dimensions, rod span). Screw geometry from CMM measurements of tested constructs. Material properties from same-lot coupon testing. Deviations: idealized thread geometry (sensitivity study shows <1.5% effect on QoIs). Equivalency established. Required level achieved."
