    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is acknowledged and accepted because the single test condition corresponds directly to the regulatory standard (ASTM F1717) and the COU is explicitly scoped to that loading configuration. All three QoIs meet quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96, relative difference < 10%). The FEA modeling framework is assessed as credible for the stated COU.",
